item.title: CVE-2020-2313|2024-08-04T07:09:54.272Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20azure%20key%20vault%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Azure Key Vault Plugin 2.0 and earlier allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to enumerate credentials IDs of credentials stored in Jenkins.
